<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.1.3">
<l>uḷḷaṉa maṟṟuḷavāppuṟamēcila māyañcolli</l>
<l>vaḷḷaṉ maṇivaṇṇaṉē yeṉṟeṉṟēyuṉṉai yumvañcikkuṅ</l>
<l>kaḷḷama ṉantavirntēyuṉaikkaṇṭukoṇ ṭuyntoḻintēṉ</l>
<l>veḷḷat taṇaikkiṭantāyiṉiyuṉṉaiviṭ ṭeṉkoḷvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Outwardly speaking a few falsehood while the things inside were others,</l>
<l>saying [and] saying “benefactor, sapphire-coloured one”, restraining [my]</l>
<l>deceptive mind that deceives you too, having seen you for myself I ended up escaping.</l>
<l>You who lieon abed in the flood, letting go of you now what would I hold on to?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
